// Generic schema header `Page<T>` carrying a `with { ... }` block whose
// method returns `Self` (i.e. `Page<T>` of the enclosing schema).
// Exercises: type parameter list on the schema header, `Self` as a
// return type.
#schema Page<T> { Int index: *, T item: * } with {
    same() -> Self: self
}
{ Page<Int> p: { index: 0, item: 7 } }
